title: Prince - Le Palace, Paris (1981) (Bootleg DVD Rip) [MP4]
description:

Dirty Mind European Tour
Theatre Le Palais, Paris
4th June 1981 (am)

Band : Prince (vox, guitar), Bobby Z. (drums), AndrÐ¹ Cymone (bass), Dez Dickerson (guitar), Dr. Fink (keyboards), Lisa Coleman (keyboards)


Do It All Night   /   Why You Wanna Treat Me So Bad?   /   Gotta Broken Heart Again   /   Jack U Off   /   When You Were Mine   /   Gotta Stop (Messin' About)   /   Sexy Dancer   /   Sister   /   Still Waiting   /   Partyup   /   Dirty Mind   /  [encore]  ...Uptown (cuts in)

Known Faults: - Track 1, Do It All Night: At the top of the image there is some tape frame-wave (glitch), that gets less as it goes till by the end it's gone. This flaw does not stop the image at any time, nor affect the sound. 

- Between Track 4 Jack U Off, and Track 5 When You Were Mine: 8 seconds of blank screen, picture & sound (no music however goes missing).

- Track 12, Uptown: Cuts in at the end of the first verse/second line, with about 50 seconds missing (as are from all show video/audio versions) : no "ultra-revolution," wind-up live-intro
